      "$value": "ui-sans-serif (system: Inter / Geist Sans / SF Pro)",
      "$type": "fontFamily",
      "$description": "All UI text — body at 14px/1.43, labels and tags at 12px/1.33, navigation at 13–14px, subheadings at 16–18px, and display headings at 30px. The 30px display step is notably restrained — this system does not shout at scale; it informs through compact hierarchy"
